The '''Roper Family''' was a young family of [[Hobbits]], an offshoot of the [[Gamgee Family]].

==History==
[[Andwise Roper|Andwise Gamgee]] adopted the surname Roper in honour of the [[Ropers|family trade]], which was started two generations earlier.<ref>{{App|Gamgee}}</ref>

The Ropers stayed in their ancestral home of [[Tighfield]], while their relatives carried the Gamgee name to [[Overhill|other]] [[Hobbiton|places]] and followed other trades.

